    "tarball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/tarball/2.3.1",
    "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/ZalithLauncher/ZalithLauncher2/zipball/2.3.1",
    "body": "## Notice:\r\n- Starting from 26.2+, Mojang has introduced the Vulkan rendering engine. If your device does not support **Vulkan 1.2**, you **may** be unable to launch the latest versions of Minecraft\r\n\r\n## Updates:\r\n- Synced translations from the [Weblate project](https://hosted.weblate.org/projects/zalithlauncher2/)\r\n- Added support for configuring the graphics API within the launcher\r\n- Updated Minecraft version metadata\r\n\r\n## Fixes:\r\n- Control layout:\r\n  - Fixed abnormal multiple event triggering for toggle buttons\r\n  - Fixed incorrect handling logic for continuous key events in control layouts\r\n- Fixed issues with input method initialization and delete text event handling\r\n- Fixed issues related to cape handling logic by [youfeng](https://github.com/youfeng11)\r\n- Account management: display default player model when no account is present",
